{"tid":439553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[加薪、有工開] 2017年10月20日 財務委員會","createTime":"2017-10-18T02:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T03:21:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd859852a4628a78b3527efd17e5980029b3cf89","tid":439553,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:01:42.000Z","msg":"財務委員會會議議程<br />\n<br />\n2017年10月20日(星期五)的2次會議 <br />\n(a)\t第一次2小時的會議於下午3時正開始；及 <br />\n(b)\t第二次2小時的會議將於下午5時10分開始 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/fc/agenda/fc20171020.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Ffc%2Fagenda%2Ffc20171020.htm&d=Fp0gW9q2H3tmsIhTXVHjeSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d21549cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/fc/agenda/fc20171020.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>758CL 號工程計劃「 沙嶺墳場興建骨灰安置所、火葬場及有關設施的土地平整及相關基礎設施工程 」</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">25億6,640萬元</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>461TH 號 工 程 計 劃「 中九龍幹線－主要工程 」</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">423億 6,390萬元</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>183GK 號工程計劃「 為展開油麻地戲院第二期發展而在油麻地巧翔街重置上海街垃圾收集站及露宿者服務單位的工程 」</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2億2,970萬元</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2017-18 年度公務員薪酬調整</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(a) 首長級及高層薪金級別的公務員，加薪幅度為 1.88%，但高層<br />\n薪金級別內任何薪點均不應低於 67,270 元 ；<br />\n(b) 中層薪金級別的公務員，加薪幅度為 2.94%；以及<br />\n(c) 低層薪金級別的公務員， 加薪幅度為 2.94%。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866cddf14c54c5800ffb7724452d832e9c4b58cb","tid":439553,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:05:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>461TH 號工程計劃「中九龍幹線－主要工程 」</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">423億 6,390萬元</span><br />\n<br />\n特別注意﹕<br />\n中九龍幹線的建造工程撥款係「打尖」，上星期未有列入議程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過公墓員加人工有back date，暫時唔會有太大反對聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f7f181c0bc942a40f18bbacdd112121ef9e3fe","tid":439553,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T02:32:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e30cfe2f3c7dae887337537d20b70a25e8eb5595","tid":439553,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1b425db0016d005b057dadd9aff61874c3fb7d","tid":439553,"uid":95617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nG 持"},{"pid":"94dafb3dbc74d9da5d7b4f8e53bf88e06dce04e6","tid":439553,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T10:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12932b33f543de6e1985e0a5051dcda57295f9ca","tid":439553,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c4abb9826dc9114f4602b3586476c86774a199","tid":439553,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43352f3a36b95a637ebe3b22c9e9e9098812d9be","tid":439553,"uid":33408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T04:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>461TH 號工程計劃「中九龍幹線－主要工程 」</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">423億 6,390萬元</span><br />\n<br />\n特別注意﹕<br />\n中九龍幹線的建造工程撥款係「打尖」，上星期未有列入議程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過公墓員加人工有back date，暫時唔會有太大反對聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9 不如我扣起你地工程撚啲人工<br />\n過大半年先出比你地"},{"pid":"78b6d5459624514845082ebfb557f7ff16e0c